      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="review-block">
      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size:16px;">Mehwish Tariq</h4>
        <span class="v-badge" style="display:flex; font-size:11px; color:#777; align-items:center;">Verified Buyer</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:18px; margin-bottom:15px;">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>
        <p style="line-height:1.7; color:#333; font-size:15px;">“Love the glow! Even my friends noticed the change in my skin tone.”</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="review-block">
      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size:16px;">Danish Ali</h4>
        <span class="v-badge" style="display:flex; font-size:11px; color:#777; align-items:center;">Verified Buyer</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:18px; margin-bottom:15px;">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>
        <p style="line-height:1.7; color:#333; font-size:15px;">“The toner is gentle yet effective. My texture has visibly improved.”</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="review-block">
      <div>
        <h4 style="font-size:16px;">Hamza Raza</h4>
        <span class="v-badge" style="display:flex; font-size:11px; color:#777; align-items:center;">Verified Buyer</span>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div style="font-size:18px; margin-bottom:15px;">★ ★ ★ ★ ★</div>
        <p style="line-height:1.7; color:#333; font-size:15px;">“My skin feels hydrated and protected all day. This bundle is a game-changer.”</p>
